  "title": "Japanese Speaking Admin (Part-time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1395236]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare sales documents such as quotations and related administrative tasks</li><li>Manage data entry and processing for product quantities and pricing adjustments</li><li>Coordinate with the warehouse on inventory confirmation, goods receipt, and shipment arrangements via email</li><li>Handle email correspondence with Japan headquarters in Japanese</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Japanese language (JLPT N2 or equivalent) for liaising with Japanese-speaking stakeholders</li><li>Strong English communication skills for email correspondence</li><li>Experience in preparing import/export documentation is an added advantage.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Excel and Word</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ito (Sherpa) Yurika</p><p>EA Personnel Registration Number: R25159178</p><p>EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
